{"tid":229203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"孝子幫慈父戴綠帽","createTime":"2017-05-04T12:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T13:42:42.000Z","uid":64544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ff2ad375a554212ad143a449b5676b9a39da5f2","tid":229203,"uid":64544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:30:42.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】台灣苗栗縣發生倫常慘劇。今日凌晨，一名黃姓男子因撞見前妻衣衫不整從兒子房間出來，疑心前妻與兒子有不倫戀情，便一時激憤以利剪殺死前妻和兒子，血跡從屋內延伸到屋外。黃男語無倫次稱：「實在不得已」。目前此案被以殺人罪移送檢方偵辦。<br />\n<br />\n據警方調查，六十三歲的黃姓男子是沙發工人，因家暴傾向，已經離婚三十餘年。<span style=\"color: red;\">六十歲的前妻一直帶着三十三歲的兒子同住，時不時打零工幫扶兒子。</span>近年黃男與前妻重逢，今年二月搬來與前妻同住。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黃男告訴警方，他疑心前妻與兒子關係曖昧，不僅母子同牀，還曾看見前妻洗澡時，兒子竟進浴室。今日凌晨，前妻起牀離開房間，二十餘分鐘後才衣衫不整從兒子房間出來。</span>他便與前妻發生口角，一時氣憤就持利剪朝妻子頸部猛刺。隨後兒子聽到呼救聲，便進門和父親扭打起來。<br />\n<br />\n監視畫面顯示，黃男與兒子扭打至屋外，最後兒子負傷，逃到屋外水溝處不支倒地，路面上有血跡一路滴濺。黃男行兇後則一直呆坐在水溝旁，直到警方將他上銬後帶回警局詢問。<br />\n<br />\n據知，黃男接受警方問話時，一下說「自己兒子怎麼會殺他？」一下又說「不得已！」因他不殺兒子，兒子會殺他。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/sy/ny/api/res/1.2/56ie99JrPWqKr1T97jP3tg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://l.yimg.com/os/creatr-images/GLB/2017-05-03/89555c50-304c-11e7-aff1-83392c1396bf_KISSWIFEANDSONE_2017050322223349792_detail.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fsy%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F56ie99JrPWqKr1T97jP3tg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fl.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2017-05-03%2F89555c50-304c-11e7-aff1-83392c1396bf_KISSWIFEANDSONE_2017050322223349792_detail.jpg&h=d768fb83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%87%B7%E7%96%91%E5%89%8D%E5%A6%BB%E8%88%87%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E4%BA%82%E5%80%AB-%E5%8F%B0%E6%BC%A2%E5%89%AA%E5%88%80%E6%8F%92%E9%A0%B8%E6%AE%BA%E5%85%A9%E4%BA%BA-140900223.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2587%25B7%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25A6%25BB%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%2590%25E4%25BA%2582%25E5%2580%25AB-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%2589%25AA%25E5%2588%2580%25E6%258F%2592%25E9%25A0%25B8%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E5%2585%25A9%25E4%25BA%25BA-140900223.html&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=659eb1d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%87%B7%E7%96%91%E5%89%8D%E5%A6%BB%E8%88%87%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E4%BA%82%E5%80%AB-%E5%8F%B0%E6%BC%A2%E5%89%AA%E5%88%80%E6%8F%92%E9%A0%B8%E6%AE%BA%E5%85%A9%E4%BA%BA-140900223.html</a>"},{"pid":"94bb1642670124614f4de8d789dd5c62e656e74f","tid":229203,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:03:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"278b11a1a53740adca907798a342b095cfc45ec2","tid":229203,"uid":64544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}